data.description: Beautiful home shows like a model home is situated in the gated community of the Villages @ Eagle's Landing.  The community is located 5 minutes from I-75, shopping, medical facilities and 30 minutes from downtown Atlanta.  From the moment you enter this home you will be amazed at the condition and space.  The backyard is a true oasis complete with a Koi pond, waterfall and lush landscaping surrounded by a walled courtyard.  The lovely 2 story foyer with curved wrought iron staircase opens to a living room/library and a formal dining room.  The updated kitchen offers stainless appliances, granite counters, abundant cabinetry, island, breakfast bar and breakfast area. The kitchen opens into the 2 story great room. A beautiful sunroom is perfect for reading or relaxing.  The owner's retreat is spacious and the adjacent master bathroom has dual vanities, separate shower and ample closet space.  On the 2nd level you will find 3 bedrooms, one of which is a large bonus room which could be utilized as a theater or recreation room.  Interior features include wood flooring, built in bookcases, upgraded trim and much more.  2 car courtyard entry garage is located on the kitchen level.
